Anthony also writes regularly on Iraq for the <i><a href="http://www.isreview.org" target="_blank">International Socialist Review</a></i>, an excellent source of news and analysis of the U.S. war. His most recent article is <a href="http://www.isreview.org/issues/51/iraqtragedy.shtml" target="_blank">"The U.S. Occupation of Iraq: Act III of a Tragedy in Many Parts."</a>
